# Fuse EIP

**Fuse EIP** provides a number of open source extensions [Apache Camel](http://camel.apache.org/) and its support of the [Enterprise Integration Patterns](http://www.eaipatterns.com/).

* distributed and federated Camel routes via [Fuse Fabric](../fabric/docs/index.html)
* [Business Activity Insight](bai.html) into your Camel routes
* [C24 integration](c24io.html) for powerful data mapping with data formats like SWIFT, SEPA, FpML, TWIST, ISO 20022, CREST and FIX



